Sinful Sweets - Season 1, Episode 5




Let Them Eat Cake

Fancy Flavors is all about food with a twist, added flavors that deliver a surprise. Harry Eastwood eats a Cherry Pie with Peppercorns in Chicago, she tries some Sour Cream Pound Cake in Philadelphia and a spicy Kulfi Donut in Charleston. It's flavor all the way and Harry is in her element.
